n.%20See%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fauto-insurance%2Fmethodology%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20rate%20auto%20insurance%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20write%20unbiased%20product%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22chonce%20maddox%20photo.JPG%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e212a7d17aa3c7b2b1cabc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20Chonc%C3%A9%20Maddox.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Chonc%C3%A9%20Maddox%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20recently%20bought%20a%20used%20car%2C%20and%20I%20ended%20up%20getting%20gap%20coverage%20and%20an%20extended%20warranty.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20your%20car%20is%20totaled%20while%20you're%20still%20paying%20it%20off%2C%20gap%20coverage%20can%20be%20extremely%20valuable.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMy%20extended%20warranty%20ensures%20that%20any%20repairs%20I%20need%20will%20be%20affordable.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recently%20traded%20in%20my%20car%20for%20a%20new-to-me%20car%20from%20CarMax.%20I%20normally%20avoid%20offers%20for%20things%20like%20extended%20warranties%2C%20but%20this%20time%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20get%20gap%20insurance.%20I%20also%20got%20CarMax's%20extended%20repair%20service%2C%20MaxCare.%20I%20spent%20over%20%244%2C500%20for%20these%20two%20add-ons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20initially%20went%20in%20with%20a%20budget%20of%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%20spend%20on%20my%20vehicle%20purchase%20%E2%80%94%20my%20add-ons%20put%20me%20well%20over%20that%20amount%20by%20almost%20%245%2C000.%20However%2C%20I%20don't%20regret%20it%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EGap%20insurance%20is%20crucial%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fauto-insurance%2Fwhat-is-gap-insurance%5C%22%3EGap%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20type%20of%20car%20insurance%20that%20covers%20the%20difference%20between%20what%20you%20owe%20on%20your%20car%20loan%20or%20lease%20and%20the%20car's%20actual%20cash%20value%20in%20the%20event%20that%20your%20vehicle%20is%20totaled%20or%20stolen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECars%20tend%20to%20depreciate%20in%20value%20quickly%20after%20you%20drive%20them%20off%20the%20lot.%20If%20your%20car%20is%20totaled%20or%20stolen%2C%20your%20standard%20auto%20insurance%20policy%20will%20pay%20out%20the%20car's%20ACV%2C%20which%20is%20the%20current%20market%20value%20of%20the%20vehicle%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident.%20This%20amount%20can%20be%20significantly%20less%20than%20what%20you%20originally%20paid%20for%20the%20car%20or%20what%20you%20still%20owe%20on%20your%20loan%20or%20lease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20that's%20the%20case%2C%20you%20will%20be%20stuck%20paying%20the%20difference%20out%20of%20your%20own%20pocket%20if%20you%20still%20owe%20money%20on%20your%20car%20at%20the%20time.%20So%2C%20for%20example%2C%20let's%20say%20you%20bought%20a%20car%20for%20%2430%2C000.%20The%20current%20loan%20balance%20is%20%2425%2C000%20when%20the%20car%20gets%20totaled%20in%20an%20accident%2C%20but%20the%20actual%20cash%20value%20is%20only%20%2420%2C000%2C%20which%20is%20what%20insurance%20agrees%20to%20pay.%20You'd%20be%20stuck%20paying%20the%20remaining%20%245%2C000%20on%20your%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20something%20that%20actually%20happened%20to%20a%20friend%20of%20mine%20when%20she%20got%20into%20an%20accident%20two%20years%20ago%20and%20totaled%20her%20leased%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20still%20had%20to%20pay%20the%20lease%20amount%20on%20a%20car%20she%20no%20longer%20had%2C%20and%20her%20insurance%20didn't%20cover%20the%20entire%20amount.%20Unfortunately%2C%20she%20also%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20lawsuit%20that%20the%20other%20driver%20filed%20because%20her%20insurance%20didn't%20offer%20enough%20to%20cover%20their%20injuries%20and%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20there%20are%20also%20a%20lot%20of%20car%20accidents%20in%20my%20area%20and%20on%20the%20interstate.%20So%2C%20for%20me%2C%20paying%20%241%2C060%20extra%20for%20gap%20coverage%20and%20also%20checking%20to%20make%20sure%20my%20auto%20insurance%20coverage%20is%20sufficient%20is%20well%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fauto-insurance%2Fbest-car-insurance-companies%5C%22%3Ebest%20car%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20look%20no%20further.%20Compare%20auto%20insurance%20quotes%20from%20multiple%20providers%20with%20Coverage.com.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fauto-insurance-bridge%5C%22%3EFind%20your%20savings%20today%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%3EMaxCare%20seemed%20worth%20the%20cost%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20thing%20I%20opted%20into%20was%20MaxCare%2C%20an%20extended%20service%20plan%20offered%20by%20CarMax.%20MaxCare%20provides%20coverage%20for%20unexpected%20vehicle%20repairs%20after%20the%20manufacturer's%20warranty%20has%20expired%2C%20protecting%20you%20from%20high%20out-of-pocket%20repair%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaxCare%20covers%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20components%2C%20including%20the%20engine%2C%20transmission%2C%20drivetrain%2C%20electrical%20systems%2C%20and%20more.%20It%20also%20includes%20coverage%20for%20systems%20like%20air%20conditioning%20and%20heating%2C%20steering%2C%20suspension%2C%20and%20brakes.%20However%2C%20it%20doesn't%20cover%20regular%20maintenance%20items%2C%20wear-and-tear%20parts%20(like%20brake%20pads%20and%20tires)%2C%20or%20cosmetic%20repairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20offered%20me%20flexible%20plan%20options%2C%20and%20I%20chose%20to%20set%20it%20up%20to%20cover%20unexpected%20repairs%20and%20major%20issues%20that%20come%20up%20over%20the%20next%20100%2C000%20miles.%20This%20added%20%243%2C500%20to%20my%20loan%20amount.%20For%20coverage%20to%20kick%20in%2C%20I%20just%20need%20to%20pay%20a%20%24300%20deductible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband's%20car%20recently%20needed%20some%20electrical%20work%20done%2C%20which%20cost%20us%20around%20%24800%20alone.%20Any%20repairs%20we've%20gotten%20done%20in%20the%20past%20have%20always%20totaled%20more%20than%20%24300%20when%20you%20include%20the%20cost%20of%20labor%2C%20parts%2C%20and%20other%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20major%20mechanical%20issues%20or%20engine%20problems%20can%20cost%20several%20thousand%20dollars%20to%20repair.%20When%20that%20happens%2C%20many%20people%20just%20opt%20for%20a%20whole%20new%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20staying%20under%20budget%2C%20but%20I'd%20rather%20pay%20a%20little%20now%20than%20a%20lot%20later%20if%20anything%20unexpected%20happens%20with%20my%20car.%20However%2C%20I%20still%20like%20that%20these%20benefits%20were%20optional%20since%20everyone's%20situation%20and%20preferences%20are%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hope%20to%20keep%20this%20car%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20but%20if%20I'm%20ever%20in%20the%20market%20to%20purchase%20again%2C%20I%20plan%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20extra%20costs%20that%20go%20into%20the%20price%20of%20a%20loan%2C%20as%20they%20can%20quickly%20add%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaid-extended-car-warranty-gap-insurance-have-no-regrets-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726578002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e212a1bf0250c214928d94%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaid-extended-car-warranty-gap-insurance-have-no-regrets-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20went%20%245%2C000%20over%20my%20budget%20on%20my%20car%2C%20but%20long-term%2C%20I'll%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20benefit%20out%20of%20the%20extras%20that%20I%20got%20if%20anything%20ever%20happens%20to%20my%20car.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Chonc%C3%A9%20Maddox)%22%2C%2