d%20of%20global%20policy%20at%20Meta%2C%20said%20that%20just%20offering%20parents%20the%20option%20to%20use%20content%20controls%20hasn't%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20when%20we%20build%20these%20controls%2C%20parents%20don't%20use%20them.%20So%20we%20have%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20behavioral%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20Clegg%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2024%2Fsep%2F12%2Fparental-controls-facebook-instagram-meta-nick-clegg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20at%20an%20event%20last%20week%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWe%20as%20an%20engineering%20company%20might%20build%20these%20things%2C%20and%20then%20we%20say%20at%20events%20like%20this%3A%20'Oh%2C%20we've%20given%20parents%20choices%20to%20restrict%20the%20amount%20of%20time%20kids%20are%20%5Bonline%5D'%20%E2%80%94%20parents%20don't%20use%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20hard%20to%20imagine%20why%20the%20existing%20parental%20controls%20aren't%20popular.%20They're%20buried%20deep%20in%20the%20app%20settings%2C%20and%20you%20have%20to%20even%20be%20aware%20that%20these%20exist%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20Well-meaning%20parents%20who%20care%20deeply%20about%20their%20children's%20safety%20and%20mental%20health%20may%20have%20simply%20never%20known%20it%20was%20possible%20to%20set%20up%20these%20kinds%20of%20controls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20some%20of%20these%20features%20had%20already%20existed%20in%20some%20form%2C%20this%20is%20actually%20a%20big%20change%20%E2%80%94%20rolling%20all%20these%20piecemeal%20parental%20control%20features%20into%20one%20thing.%20Crucially%2C%20it's%20turned%20on%3Cem%3E%20by%20default.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22instagram%20teen%20account%20features%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e89c86bf0250c21493ec8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221279%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETeen%20Accounts%20will%20have%20%26quot%3BSleep%20Mode%26quot%3B%20enabled%20by%20default.%20For%20younger%20teens%2C%20parents%20can%20see%20who%20they%20DM%20with.%3Cp%3EInstagram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETeen%20Accounts%20will%20have%20%26quot%3BSleep%20Mode%26quot%3B%20at%20night%20%E2%80%94%20and%20at%20all%20times%20of%20the%20day%2C%20the%20accounts%20will%20have%20a%20reminder%20that%20pops%20up%20to%20take%20a%20break%20after%20an%20hour%20of%20use.%20Accounts%20will%20be%20defaulted%20to%20private%20settings%20and%20won't%20allow%20strangers%20to%20message%20or%20tag%20them.%20For%20younger%20teens%2C%20parents%20can%20see%20who%20their%20children%20direct%20message%20with%20%E2%80%94%20but%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20read%20their%20DMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETeens%20under%2016%20will%20need%20parental%20permission%20to%20opt%20out%20of%20these%20more%20restrictive%20settings.%20Accounts%20of%2016-%20and%2017-year-olds%20will%20automatically%20default%20to%20Teen%20Accounts%2C%20but%20they'll%20be%20able%20to%20change%20the%20settings%20on%20their%20own%20(unless%20a%20parent%20has%20already%20signed%20onto%20parental%20controls).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20although%20age%20is%20self-reported%2C%20Meta%20already%20has%20been%20using%20AI%20to%20help%20detect%20if%20someone%20is%20under%2018.%20It%20says%20it%20is%20building%20tools%20to%20find%20accounts%20where%20kids%20lied%20about%20their%20age%20at%20signup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20certainly%20is%20aware%20that%20it%20has%20a%20perception%20problem%20with%20teen%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagram-scandal-crisis-era-mark-zuckerberg-lawsuit-child-predator-report-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%20head%20Adam%20Mosseri%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20internal%20email%20that%20was%20unearthed%20in%20recent%20lawsuits%20filed%20by%20a%20group%20of%20states%20against%20the%20company%3A%20%26quot%3BSocial%20comparison%20is%20to%20Instagram%20%5Bwhat%5D%20election%20inter