ait%2C%20given%20the%20upcoming%20Durga%20Puja%20celebrations%2C%20she%20announced%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20Commissioner%20would%20be%20replaced%2C%20as%20would%20the%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20(North%20Division)%20and%20the%20two%20health%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20after%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20she%20had%20accepted%2099%25%20of%20the%20doctors'%20%26quot%3Bdemands%20because%20they%20are%20our%20younger%20brothers%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20had%20become%20more%20vocal%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20Commissioner%20after%20the%20CBI%20arrested%20Dr%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20former%20principal%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20and%20Abhijit%20Mondal%2C%20officer-in-charge%20of%20Tala%20Police%20Station%20(under%20which%20the%20RG%20Kar%20Hospital%20falls)%20last%20week%20and%20alleged%20that%20they%20tampered%20with%20evidence.%20This%20lent%20credence%20to%20the%20doctors'%20claim%20that%20the%20case%20was%20not%20handled%20properly%20by%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20and%20there%20was%20an%20attempted%20cover-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20their%20agitation%20entered%20its%2039th%20day%2C%20the%20doctors%20said%20earlier%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20state%20government%20accepting%20their%20demands%20was%20a%20big%20victory%20but%20a%20final%20call%20on%20withdrawing%20their%20agitation%20would%20be%20taken%20only%20after%20the%20state%20government%20implements%20its%20announcements%20%26quot%3Bin%20true%20spirit%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726572240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fp5rcq3bo_manoj-kumar-verma-ips_625x300_17_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-police-commissioner-replaced-on-doctors-demands-manoj-kumar-verma-takes-over-6585243%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20West%20Bengal%20government%20has%20transferred%20Kolkata%20Police%20Commissioner