o%20pick%20up%20and%20values%20are%20beginning%20to%20stabilize%20in%20the%20real%20estate%20sector.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECBRE%20forecasts%20that%20commercial%20sales%20activity%20will%20rebound%20to%20%24322%20billion%20of%20transactions%20in%202024%20as%20a%20result%20and%20to%20%24387%20billion%20in%202025%2C%20a%205%25%20and%2026%25%20increase%20from%202023's%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%202013%20and%202022%2C%20deal%20activity%20averaged%20%24460%20billion%20a%20year%20nationally%2C%20according%20to%20CBRE%2C%20with%20volume%20peaking%20during%20a%20surge%20in%20sales%20in%202021%2C%20when%20nearly%20%24740%20billion%20transactions%20were%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228ffffdc7-028b-4ac6-8bb7-38ac691d197e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20damage%20done%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20full%20recovery%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20still%20a%20long%20way%20off.%20Rising%20interest%20rates%20brought%20down%20commercial%20values%20by%20about%2019%25%20from%20their%20most%20recent%20peaks%2C%20according%20to%20a%20price%20index%20published%20by%20Green%20Street%2C%20a%20real%20estate%20data%20firm%2C%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deteriorating%20prices%20also%20meant%20that%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20of%20in-place%20mortgage%20debts%20grew%20outsize%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20new%20reduced%20values%2C%20making%20loans%20difficult%20to%20refinance%20at%20maturity%20and%20pushing%20up%20defaults%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Fitch%20projected%20that%20commercial%20mortgage%20backed%20security%20delinquency%20rates%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20would%20rise%20from%202.3%25%20in%20February%20to%204.5%25%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%20and%20to%204.9%25%20in%202025%2C%20due%20in%20part%20to%20increased%20maturity%20defaults.%20In%202023%2C%20total%20CMBS%20defaults%20rose%20to%20encompass%20%248.6%20billion%20of%20debt%2C%20up%20more%20than%20double%20from%20%243.2%20billion%20in%202022%2C%20Fitch%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECMBS%20is%20just%20a%20small%20segment%20of%20the%20commercial%20lending%20market.%20There%20is%20%245.9%20trillion%20of%20outstanding%20commercial%20real%20estate%20debt%2C%20of%20which%20%24694%20billion%20is%20securitized%2C%20totaling%20less%20than%2012%25%20of%20the%20overall%20market%2C%20according%20to%20the%20data%20from%20Trepp.%20Half%20is%20held%20by%20banks%20%E2%80%93%20although%20many%20have%20been%20eager%20to%20sidestep%20today's%20problems%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbanks-commercial-real-estate-loan-sales-debt-interest-rates-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eby%20extending%20debts%2C%20even%20at%20below-market%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20about%20%241.5%20trillion%20of%20loans%20is%20due%20to%20expire%20in%202024%20and%202025%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Mortgage%20Bankers%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERate%20cuts%20are%20expected%20to%20give%20a%20lift%20to%20property%20values%2C%20diminishing%20the%20amount%20of%20additional%20equity%20landlords%20must%20invest%20to%20bridge%20gaps%20between%20in-place%20mortgages%20and%20new%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20anticipation%20of%20the%20Fed%20rate%20cuts%2C%20average%20commercial%20mortgage%20rates%20have%20already%20fallen%20to%20around%207%25%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20compared%20with%20a%20peak%20of%207.5%25%20in%20October%202023%20(and%20up%20from%203.5%25%20in%20September%202021).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20signs%20that%20refinancings%20are%20picking%20up%20as%20a%20result.%20In%202023%2C%20%24430%20billion%20of%20commercial%20mortgage%20originations%20were%20completed%2C%20according%20to%20the%20MBA%2C%2047%25%20less%20in%20dollar%20volume%20than%202022.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20MBA%20projects%20that%20%24539%20billion%20of%20originations%20will%20be%20completed%20%E2%80%93%20a%20roughly%2023%25%20increase%20year-over-year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProperty%20prices%20are%20also%20already%20bouncing%20back%2C%20according%20to%20some%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreen%20Street's%20property%20price%20index%20rose%201.6%25%20in%20August%2C%20it%20said%2C%20and%20has%20increased%203.3%25%20so%20far%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCommercial%20property%20prices%20have%20increased%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%20as%20bond%20yields%20have%20declined%2C%26quot%3B%20Peter%20Rothemund%2C%20the%20co-head%20of%20strategic%20research%20at%20Green%20Street%2C%20said%20in%20the%20firm's%20recent%20property%20pricing%20report.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20good%20chance%20the%20momentum%20in%20pricing%20continues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2223dbc2f4-d91a-462e-b54e-5739555efad2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EReasons%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20office%20market%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOptimism%20for%20an%20office%20rebound%20is%20more%20complicated.%20The%20segment%20was%20battered%20not%20only%20by%20higher%20rates%2C%20but%20a%20lasting%20embrace%20of%20remote%20work%20that%20has%20created%20lingering%20vacancy%20rates%2C%20especially%20in%20older%2C%20less-amenitized%20office%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFitch%20has%20predicted%20CMBS%20delinquency%20rates%20for%20office%20buildings%20could%20jump%20to%208.1%25%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%20from%203.6%25%20in%20February%2C%20and%20to%209.9%25%20in%202025%2C%20a%20rate%20that%20would%20exceed%20default%20rates%20for%20offices%20during%20the%20financial%20crisis%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20pockets%20of%20the%20debt%20market%20have%20also%20been%20hit%20hard.%20Securitized%20floating%20rate%20debts%20taken%20by%20property%20buyers%20to%20acquire%20speculative%20investments%20have%20also%20struggled.%20Default%20rates%20for%20these%20collateralized%20debt%20obligations%2C%20or%20CLOs%2C%20have%20jumped%20to%209.3%25%20from%201.85%25%20in%202021%2C%20according%20to%20Bank%20of%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoans%20against%20apartment%20buildings%20make%20up%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20roughly%20%2480%20billion%20of%20outstanding%20CLO%20debts.%20The%20loans%20were%20taken%20for%20deals%20that%20sometimes%20involved%20repositioning%20a%20property%20to%20achieve%20higher%20rents%20%E2%80%93%20business%20plans%20that%20stumbled%20in%20some%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20you%20were%20or%20were%20not%20able%20to%20renovate%20the%20property%20as%20quickly%20%E2%80%93%20maybe%20your%20expenses%20ramped%20up%20more%20than%20you%20thought%2C%26quot%3B%20Alan%20Todd%2C%20the%20head%20of%20CMBS%20research%20at%20Bank%20of%20America%20Securities%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETodd%20said%20he%20believed%20that%20rate%20cuts%20might%20help%20some%20ailing%20CLO%20deals%2C%20but%20that%20cuts%20alone%20were%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20cure-all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20better%20properties%2C%20better%20operators%20who%20were%20at%20the%20margin%20will%20be%20okay%2C%26quot%3B%20Todd%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20you're%20going%20to%20have%20a%20tail%20of%20properties%20that%20don't%20make%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommercial-real-estate-federal-reserve-interest-rate-cuts-rebound-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726570802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e88cfbd17aa3c7b2b325b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommercial-real-estate-federal-reserve-interest-rate-cuts-rebound-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Fed%20brought%20rates%20up%20beginning%20in%202022%2C%20heavily%20affecting%20commercial%20real%20estate%20values.%20With%20cuts%20on%20the%20way%2C%20the%20market%20could%20now%20bounce%20back.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dgeiger%40businessinsider.com%20(Daniel%20Geiger)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommercial-real-estate-federal-reserve-interest-rate-cuts-rebound-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHuge%20Focus%20On%20Safety%26quot%3B%3A%20Railways%20Minister's%20Report%20On%20Modi%203.0's%20100%20Days%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20set%20an%20aggressive%20target%20for%20implementing%20the%20Kavach%20train%20protection%20system%20across%20the%20rail%20network%20in%20the%20next%20five%20to%20six%20years%2C%20Railways%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20told%20NDTV%20as%20Modi%203.0%20completed%20100%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20Mr%20Vaishnaw%20said%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20took%20historic%20initiatives%20in%20the%20first%20and%20second%20terms%20and%20set%20the%20foundation%20for%20India%20to%20become%20a%20developed%20country%20by%202047.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20election%20process%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20called%20all%20the%20bureaucrats%20and%20told%20them%20that%20the%20country's%20progress%20should%20not%20stop.%20He%20told%20the%20officials%20that%20we%20would%20be%20busy%20with%20elections%2C%20but%20they%20should%20keep%20planning.%20Because%20of%20this%20vision%2C%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20announce%20many%20new%20programmes%20and%20start%20new%20work%20in%20100%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E100-Day%20Report%20Card%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20how%20his%20ministry%20has%20performed%20in%20the%20first%20100%20days%20of%20Modi%203.0%2C%20Mr%20Vaishnaw%20said%20Railways%20has%20started%2012%20new%20projects%20with%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Railways%20Minister%20said%20the%20government%20is%20focusing%20on%20improving%20the%20travel%20experience%20of%20lower-income%20and%20middle-income%20groups.%20He%20said%20they%20are%20adding%20general%20coaches%20that%20cater%20to%20lower-income%20groups.%20%26quot%3B108%20trains%20have%20been%20augmented%20with%20new%20general%20coaches%20and%2012%2C500%20new%20general%20coaches%20are%20being%20manufactured%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20NaMo%20Bharat%20Rapid%20Rail%20service%2C%20the%20first%20of%20which%20was%20inaugurated%20between%20Ahmedabad%20and%20Bhuj%20yesterday%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20going%20to%20be%20revolutionary%20because%2C%20at%20a%20very%20low%20cost%2C%20a%20very%20high-quality%20service%20will%20be%20provided%20to%20commuters%20travelling%20from%20one%20city%20to%20another.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Railways'%20infrastructure%20push%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20the%20world's%20highest%20rail%20arch%20bridge%2C%20Chenab%20Bridge%2C%20has%20been%20commissioned%2C%20900%20km%20of%20new%20tracks%20commissioned%2C%20and%20100%20digital%20stations%20and%20309%20locomotives%20are%20in%20the%20works%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vaishnaw%20said%20the%20Railways%20has%20introduced%20a%20direct%20drive%20technology%20based%20on%20the%20lessons%20learned%20from%20the%20Balasore%20accident%20that%20left%20nearly%20300%20people%20dead.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20Balasore%20accident%2C%20there%20was%20manipulation%20in%20the%20electrical%20panel%20that%20controls%20point%20machines%2C%20so%20we%20decided%20to%20change%20the%20entire%20technology.%20The%20first%20direct%20drive%20technology%20has%20now%20been%20introduced%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20said%20that%2058%2C642%20vacancies%20have%20been%20notified%20for%20recruitment%20in%20Railways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Railways%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20neglected%20throughout%20the%20Congress%20rule.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20considered%20a%20political%20tool%2C%20not%20a%20department%20which%20can%20bring%20about%20a%20big%20change%20in%20people's%20lives.%20That%20is%20the%20change%20which%20has%20happened%20during%20PM%20Modi's%20tenure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeeting%20High%20Demand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20demand%20for%20rail%20travel%20is%20increasing%20every%20day%20and%20the%20government%20is%20bringing%20about%20a%20massive%20augmentation%20of%20its%20infrastructure%20to%20meet%20this%20demand%2C%20Ms%20Vaishnaw%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20manufacturing%20of%20trains%20has%20significantly%20increased%20if%20you%20compare%20it%20with%20the%20UPA%20period.%20We%20are%20now%20manufacturing%20close%20to%206%2C000%20coaches%20a%20year.%20During%20UPA%2C%20it%20was%202000-3000%2C%20close%20to%201200%20locomotives%20are%20now%20being%20manufactured%2C%20compared%20to%20200-300%20a%20year%20during%20UPA.%20Massive%20change%20has%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20festive%20season%20round%20the%20corner%2C%20the%20Railways%20has%20decided%20to%20deploy%20a%20record%20number%20of%20special%20trains%20to%20tackle%20the%20rush%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20people%20from%20low-income%20groups%2C%20we%20have%20introduced%20Amrit%20Bharat%20trains%20with%20the%20same%20features%20as%20Vande%20Bharat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20two%20such%20trains%20were%20launched%20in%20January%20and%20one%20will%20be%20launched%20every%20week%20from%20October%20onwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVande%20Bharat%20vs%20Other%20Trains%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECounting%20the%20charge%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20is%20promoting%20Vande%20Bharat%20trains%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20other%20trains%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOther%20trains%20are%20absolutely%20(getting)%20much%20higher%20focus%20compared%20to%20Vande%20Bharat.%20It's%20just%20that%20Vande%20Bharat%20is%20catching%20the%20imagination%20of%20the%20people.%20That's%20why%20there%20is%20so%20much%20excitement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20we%20as%20Railways%20are%20very%20much%20focused%20on%20making%20sure%20that%20the%20lowest%20income%20categories%20of%20the%20society%20get%20very%20affordable%20rail%20travel%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2016%20new%20Vande%20Bharat%20trains%20had%20been%20launched%20in%20the%2010%20days%20of%20Modi%203.0%20and%20the%20first%2020-coach%20Vande%20Bharat%20has%20been%20rolled%20out.%20Vande%20Bharat%20sleeper%20trains%20are%20going%20for%20testing%20and%20trials%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BHuge%20Focus%20On%20Safety%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20repeatedly%20criticised%20Mr%20Vaishnaw%20over%20the%20Railways'%20safety%20record%20and%20train%20derailments.%20Responding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20how%20the%20national%20transporter%20plans%20to%20tackle%20safety%20issues%2C%20the%20minister%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20made%20sure%20that%20each%20and%20every%20incident%20that%20happens%20in%20Railways%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20an%20accident%20or%20other%20incident%2C%20we%20go%20to%20the%20root%20cause.%20Wherever%20systemic%20changes%20have%20to%20be%20made%2C%20we%20make%20them%2C%20wherever%20procedural%20improvements%20have%20to%20be%20done%2C%20we%20do%20that%2C%20and%20where%20technology%20has%20to%20be%20changed%2C%20we%20are%20changing%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20done%2097%2C000%20inspections%2C%20verified%2090%2C000%20signal%20plans%2C%202%2C500%20km%20of%20tracks%20(have%20been)%20renewed.%20Ultrasound%20testing%20is%20being%20done%20for%20the%20entire%20railway%20network.%20This%20fiscal%2C%201%2C86%2C000%20km%20of%20tracks%20have%20been%20checked%20with%20ultrasound%20machines%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20stressing%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20focus%20on%20safety%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Centre's%20much-touted%20Kavach%20train%20protection%20system%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20the%20Congress%20governments%20could%20not%20do%20in%2058%20years%2C%20within%20a%20short%20time-frame%20of%2010%20years%2C%20we%20got%20this%20new%20technology%20developed%2C%20tested%20and%20the%20deployment%20started.%20The%20first%20tender%20was%20done%20in%202022%2C%20out%20of%20that%20632%20km%20is%20already%20commissioned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVersion%204%20of%20Kavach%20was%20approved%20on%20July%2016%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20government%20has%20put%20out%20tenders%20for%2010%2C000%20locomotives%20and%209%2C600%20km%20of%20train%20trains.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20happy%20to%20share%20that%20yesterday%2C%20the%20first%20section%20with%20Kavach%204.0%20got%20commissioned%20between%20Kota%20and%20Sawai%20Madhopur%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20with%20the%20system%20in%20place%2C%20the%20driver%20can%20see%20the%20signal%20from%20several%20kilometres%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20a%20timeline%20for%20this%20system%20being%20implemented%20across%20the%20Railway%20network%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20countries%20which%20have%20half%20or%20less%20than%20half%20of%20our%20network%20size%20took%20about%2015.20%20years.%20But%20our%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20given%20us%20a%20very%20aggressive%20target.%20We%20would%20like%20to%20cover%20the%20whole%20network%20within%205-6%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726570740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fc6ldch6o_ashwini-vaishnaw-interview_625x300_17_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fashwini-vaishnaw-interview-huge-focus-on-safety-railways-ministers-report-on-modi-3-0s-100-days-6585558%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20set%20an%20aggressive%20target%20for%20implementing%20the%20Kavach%20train%20protection%20system%20across%20the%20rail%20network%20in%20the%20next%20five%20to%20six%20years%2C%20Railways%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20told%20NDTV%20as%20Modi%203.0%20completed%20100%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2