s%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fbangladesh-in-india%2Fno-need-for-different-says-india-skipper-rohit-sharma-ahead-of-first-bangladesh-test%2Farticleshow%2F113425497.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20asserts%20that%20no%20new%20strategy%20is%20needed%20against%20Bangladesh%20despite%20their%20recent%20win%20over%20Pakistan.%20He%20emphasizes%20focusing%20on%20India's%20gameplay%20and%20managing%20bowlers'%20workloads.%20Rohit%20also%20highlights%20the%20importance%20of%20nurturing%20young%20talents%20like%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20and%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20for%20future%20success%20in%20all%20formats%20of%20the%20game.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fbangladesh-in-india%2Fno-need-for-different-says-india-skipper-rohit-sharma-ahead-of-first-bangladesh-test%2Farticleshow%2F113425497.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BGlorification%2C%20Grandstanding%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Pauses%20'Bulldozer%20Justice'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsupreme-court%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%20halted%20unauthorised%20demolition%20of%20private%20property%2C%20anywhere%20in%20India%2C%20till%20October%201%2C%20when%20it%20will%20next%20hear%20arguments%20against%20'%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fbulldozer-justice%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebulldozer%20justice%3C%2Fa%3E'%20-%20the%20practice%20by%20some%20state%20governments%20to%20destroy%20residential%20or%20commercial%20property%20owned%20by%20people%20accused%20in%20criminal%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20dismissed%20concerns%20by%20the%20government%20-%20represented%20by%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20-%20that%20its%20order%20would%20impact%20legally%20sanctioned%20demolitions.%20%26quot%3BThe%20heavens%20won't%20fall%20if%20we%20ask%20you%20to%20hold%20your%20hands%20till%20(the)%20next%20hearing%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20KV%20Viswanathan%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20irate%20top%20court%20-%20which%20has%20already%20come%20down%20hard%2C%20twice%20this%20month%2C%20on%20'bulldozer%20justice'%20-%20also%20warned%20against%20%26quot%3Bgrandstanding%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bglorification%26quot%3B%20of%20this%20practice.%20%26quot%3BNo%20demolition%2C%20till%20next%2C%20date%2C%20without%20permission%20of%20this%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20warning%20the%20Election%20Commission%20may%20be%20put%20on%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reference%20to%20the%20poll%20panel%20is%20significant%20given%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-elections-news%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAssembly%20elections%20this%20week%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%20(the%20first%20in%20a%20decade)%20and%20in%20Haryana%20next%20month%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20looking%20to%20return%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20waved%20away%20Mr%20Mehta's%20suggestion%20it%20had%20been%20influenced%20by%20a%20%26quot%3Bnarrative%26quot%3B%2C%20pointing%20out%20%26quot%3Beven%20if%20there%20is%20one%20instance%20of%20illegal%20demolition%2C%20it%20is%20against%20the%20ethos%20of%20the%20Constitution%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20'narrative'%20is%20not%20influencing%20us.%20We%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20we%20won't%20(stop)%20demolition%20of%20unauthorised%20construction...%20but%20the%20executive%20can't%20be%20a%20'judge'%20(of%20what%20is%20illegal)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%2C%20saying%2C%20once%20again%2C%20that%C2%A0it%20will%20also%20lay%20down%20guidelines%20to%20identify%20potentially%20illegal%20constructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20-%20hearing%20petitions%20against%20those%20whose%20homes%20had%20been%20bulldozed%20-%20also%20said%20its%20order%20is%20not%20applicable%20to%20removing%20encroachments%20in%20public%20spaces%20like%20roads%2C%20railway%20tracks%2C%20and%20water%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BNarrative-Building%26quot%3B%2C%20Says%20Centre%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20today's%20hearing%20some%20petitioners%20said%20demolition%20had%20taken%20place%20despite%20the%20court's%20earlier%20instructions%20-%20that%20%26quot%3Balleged%20involvement%20in%20a%20crime%20is%20no%20ground%20for%20demolition%20of%20property%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20happening%20daily...%20please%20give%20a%20short%20date%20(to%20the%20next%20hearing).%20That%20is%20all%20I%20am%20saying...%26quot%3B%20one%20petitioner%20said%2C%20while%20another%20asked%20how%20%26quot%3Bin%20a%20neighbourhood%20only%20one%20house%20is%20'unauthorised'%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Mr%20Mehta%C2%A0had%20referred%20to%20demolitions%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20to%20counter%20claims%20that%20bulldozers%20were%20used%20to%20target%20property%20belonging%20to%20non-Hindus%2C%20specifically%20Muslim%2C%20community%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh...%2070%20shops%20were%20demolished%20after%20following%20procedure%20and%20more%20than%2050%20belonged%20to%20Hindus.%20What%20they%20are%20saying%20-%20'mohallas'%2C%20etc.%20-%20is%20just%20'narrative%20building'!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20narrative%20has%20appealed%20to%20this%20court...%26quot%3B%20the%20Solicitor%20General%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mehta%20also%20told%20the%20court%20bulldozing%20of%20certain%20properties%20-%20whose%20owners%20had%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20-%20took%20place%20two%20years%20after%20notice%20had%20been%20issued.%20%26quot%3BIn%20between%2C%20offences%20were%20committed...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BLike%20Bulldozing%20Laws%20Of%20Country%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20the%20court%20said%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20a%20crime%20could%20not%20be%20a%20reason%20to%20demolish%20property%20owned%20by%20that%20individual%2C%20and%20that%20such%20action%20was%20like%20%26quot%3Bbulldozing%20the%20laws%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20-%20a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Hrishikesh%20Roy%2C%20Justice%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%2C%20and%20Justice%20SVN%20Bhatti%20-%20was%20hearing%20a%20plea%20from%20Gujarat's%20Kheda%20district%2C%20which%20said%20municipal%20officers%C2%A0had%20threatened%20to%20demolish%20a%20man's%20home%20after%20a%20trespassing%20case%20was%20filed%20against%20him.%20That%20plea%20cited%20the%20top%20court's%20September%202%20order%2C%20in%20which%20it%20had%20proposed%20a%20set%20of%20guidelines%20to%20be%20followed%20before%20demolishing%20homes.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flike-bulldozing-laws-of-country-supreme-court-on-bulldozer-justice-6551111%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBulldozing%20Laws%20Of%20Country...%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20On%20'Bulldozer%20Justice'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20September%202%2C%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Gavai%20and%20Justice%20Viswanathan%20had%20asked%20how%20a%20house%20could%20be%20demolished%20just%20because%20it%20belongs%20to%20an%20accused%20or%20even%20a%20convict%20in%20a%20criminal%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20observation%20was%20key%20given%20the%20frequency%20with%20which%20some%20states%20rush%20out%20bulldozers%3B%20recent%20examples%20include%20Jaipur%2C%20where%20a%20house%20was%20destroyed%20because%20the%20owner's%20son%20stabbed%20a%20classmate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fakhilesh-yadav-yogi-aditya