ess-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Feasemytrip-enters-medical-tourism-board-approves-rs-90-crore-acquisitions-124091700578_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Americans%20are%20piling%20into%20a%20hot%20new%20type%20of%20ETF%20investing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20stock%20traders%20on%20the%20floor.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e88d1abf0250c21493e313%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20M.%20Santiago%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EETFs%20have%20surged%20in%20popularity%2C%20with%20net%20inflows%20of%20%24539%20billion%20in%202023%2C%20per%20JPMorgan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EModel%20portfolios%20using%20ETFs%20have%20grown%2C%20doubling%20assets%20under%20management%20from%202016%20to%202023.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJPMorgan's%20chief%20ETF%20strategy%20detailed%20the%20positives%20of%20ETF%20model%20portfolios.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20popularity%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-an-etf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexchange-traded%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20skyrocketed%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20as%20more%20Americans%20have%20opted%20for%20them%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fmutual-funds%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emutual%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20two%20vehicles%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fetf-vs-mutual-fund%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estructured%20similarly%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20appeal%20of%20ETFs%20has%20long%20been%20lower%20fees%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20be%20actively%20traded%20like%20stocks.%20This%20dynamic%20was%20reflected%20in%20fund-flows%20data%20for%202023%2C%20which%20saw%20net%20inflows%20for%20mutual%20funds%20fall%20%24462%20billion%20as%20ETFs%20absorbed%20a%20net%20%24539%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20JPMorgan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20between%202014%20and%202024%2C%20assets%20under%20management%20in%20ETFs%20were%20at%2016%25%2C%20versus%2084%25%20for%20mutual%20funds.%20As%20of%20June%202024%2C%20it%20was%2032%25%20for%20ETFs%20to%2068%25%20for%20mutual%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20trend%20that's%20expected%20to%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20becoming%20pretty%20clear%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20investors%20are%20now%20viewing%20ETFs%20as%20their%20vehicle%20of%20choice%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Matt%20Barry%2C%20head%20of%20capital%20markets%20at%20Touchstone%20Investments%2C%20a%20firm%20that%20manages%20mutual%20funds%20and%20ETFs.%20He%20added%20that%20their%20structural%20benefits%2C%20including%20tax%20efficiency%2C%20transparency%2C%20and%20liquidity%2C%20have%20been%20driving%20that%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221634%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20charts%20demonstrating%20assets%20under%20management%20ratios%20and%20flows%20between%20mutual%20funds%20and%20ETFs.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e8690fbf0250c21493cb21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22986%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGuide%20to%20ETFs%2C%20JP%20Morgan%20Asset%20Management%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b2186448-9b99-4c7a-aad3-6e9c828d7a24%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20new%20ETF%20strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20the%20ETF%20space%2C%20institutional%20interest%20has%20grown%20over%20time%2C%20and%20a%20popular%20new%20strategy%20has%20emerged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20increased%20number%20of%20money%20managers%20are%20choosing%20to%20offer%20so-called%20model%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eportfolios%20using%20ETFs%20as%20the%20main%20vehicles.%20The%20overall%20goal%20of%20a%20model%20portfolio%20is%20to%20match%20a%20client's%20collection%20of%20assets%20with%20a%20predetermined%20objective%20%E2%80%94%20anything%20from%20growth%20to%20income%20to%20capital%20preservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20pick%20a%20collection%20of%20funds%20themselves%2C%20the%20clients%20of%20the%20model%20portfolios%20leave%20the%20mix%20of%20ETFs%20up%20to%20professional%20investment%20advisors%2C%20depending%20on%20what%20they%20want%20to%20achieve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJon%20Maier%2C%20chief%20ETF%20strategist%20at%20JPMorgan%2C%20outlined%20a%20few%20more%20advantages.%20Instead%20of%20deploying%20a%20large%20team%20of%20analysts%20to%20scour%20through%20stocks%20and%20fixed-income%20products%20or%20paying%20hefty%20hedge%20fund%20fees%2C%20they%20use%20an%20ETF%20that%20does%20something%20similar%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20a%20more%20user-friendly%20and%20efficient%20way%20to%20manage%20assets%2C%20said%20Maier.%20For%20one%2C%20scalability%20is%20easier%20since%20management%20teams%20aren't%20directly%20responsible%20for%20overseeing%20every%20asset%20in%20the%20portfolio.%20Instead%2C%20they%20can%20leverage%20the%20expertise%20of%20the%20investment%20management%20teams%20of%20each%20specialized%20ETF%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20works%20well%20since%20there%20is%20now%20an%20ETF%20for%20just%20about%20anything%3A%20from%20those%20that%20passively%20track%20a%20broad%20index%20to%20those%20that%20actively%20manage%20a%20strategy%20or%20grouping%20of%20securities.%20They%20can%20be%20built%20around%20a%20theme%20like%20AI%20or%20a%20sector%20like%20healthcare.%20They%20can%20also%20be%20focused%20on%20types%20of%20stocks%20like%20growth%2C%20value%2C%20or%20dividend-payers.%20And%20if%20you%20want%20to%20balance%20or%20hedge%20a%20portfolio%2C%20there%20are%20ETFs%20that%20manage%20fixed%20income%20or%20employ%20options%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we've%20seen%20over%20the%20past%20five%20or%20so%20years%20since%20the%20ETF%20level%20came%20up%2C%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20active%20managers%20getting%20into%20the%20ETF%20space%26quot%3B%2C%20Barry%20said%2C%20who%20has%20witnessed%20active%20funds%20go%20from%20a%20small%20sliver%20of%20the%20ETF%20universe%20to%20making%20up%20a%20quarter%20of%20net%20inflows%20coming%20into%20the%20space.%20This%20means%20managers%20opting%20for%20the%20ETF%20model%20portfolios%20have%20a%20range%20of%20active%20funds%20and%20expertise%20to%20choose%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWord%20seems%20to%20have%20gotten%20out%20in%20recent%20years.%20Between%202016%20to%202023%2C%20assets%20under%20management%20in%20model%20portfolios%20more%20than%20doubled%2C%20going%20from%20%242.1%20trillion%20to%20%245.1%20trillion%2C%20according%20to%20JPMorgan's%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22962%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chart%20that%20demonstrates%20allocation%20growth%20in%20model%20portfolios.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e869d4cfb7f307e571fe55%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22694%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGuide%20to%20ETFs%2C%20JP%20Morgan%20Asset%20Management%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20inflow%20to%20model%20portfolios%20isn't%20purely%20ETFs%2C%20Maier%20said.%20It's%20a%20combination%20of%20ETFs%2C%20mutual%20funds%2C%20and%20separate%20accounts%20that%20are%20merged%20into%20a%20strategy.%20He%20acknowledged%20that%20it's%20difficult%20to%20parse%20out%20how%20much%20of%20it%20is%20purely%20ETFs.%20However%2C%20since%20the%20US's%20compounded%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%20assets%20piling%20into%20ETFs%20is%20at%2017%25%2C%20from%20a%20trend%20and%20anecdotal%20perspective%2C%20he%20assumes%20much%20of%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaier%2C%20who%20once%20ran%20Merrill%20Lynch's%20model%20portfolios%2C%20says%20that%20most%20firms%20that%20chose%20to%20employ%20this%20structure%20aren't%20just%20buying%20up%20ETFs%20with%20the%20appropriate%20exposure.%20There's%20still%20a%20bottom-up%20approach%20that%20requires%20them%20to%20look%20under%20the%20hood%20and%20assess%20the%20allocation%20of%20the%20securities%20while%20navigating%20macroeconomic%20trends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20in%20the%20context%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-diversification%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%2060-40%20stock-to-bond%3C%2Fa%3E%20portfolio%2C%20a%20money%20manager%20could%20use%20various%20ETFs%20to%20satisfy%20each%20division.%20In%20equities%2C%20they%20can%20balance%20passive%20and%20active%20funds%20with%20exposure%20to%20growth%20or%20value%20depending%20on%20an%20investor's%20risk%20appetite.%20They%20could%20overweight%20a%20sector%20based%20on%20the%20business%20cycle%20or%20pick%20funds%20with%20an%20international%20component%2C%20Maier%20noted.%20A%20similar%20approach%20can%20be%20employed%20for%20the%20fixed-income%20side%20by%20picking%20ETFs%20that%20target%20a%20particular%20duration%20or%20credit%20quality%20and%20shifting%20that%20allocation%20over%20time%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaier%20noted%20that%20the%20tax%20efficiency%20of%20ETFs%20is%20another%20benefit%20since%20managers%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20capital%20gains%20every%20time%20they%20turn%20over%20a%20position.%20As%20for%20fees%2C%20while%20each%20fund%20will%20vary%2C%20it's%20typically%20a%20layer%20of%20those%20charged%20by%20the%20underlying%20ETFs%20and%20a%20management%20or%20wrapper%20fee%20that%20could%20range%20between%200.5%25%20to%201%25%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvesting-in-etf-model-portfolios-advantages-over-mutual-funds-jpmorgan-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726569302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e8705acfb7f307e57203e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%