ion%20attempt%20against%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20show%20the%20Secret%20Service%20is%20stretched%20so%20thin%20due%20to%20short%20staffing%20that%20potential%20dangers%20are%20becoming%20increasingly%20hard%20to%20respond%20to%20adequately%2C%20two%20former%20agents%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Monday%20press%20conference%20discussing%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20acting%20director%20of%20the%20Secret%20Service%20called%20for%20%26quot%3Bsome%20hard%20conversations%20with%20Congress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20president%20was%20unharmed%20on%20Sunday%20after%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-ryan-wesley-routh-second-trump-assassination-attempt-suspect-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewould-be%20shooter%3C%2Fa%3E%20hiding%20in%20the%20perimeter%20treeline%20of%20the%20Trump%20International%20Golf%20Club%20West%20Palm%20Beach%20was%20spotted%20and%20fired%20upon%20by%20a%20Secret%20Service%20agent.%20The%20suspect%20was%20able%20to%20flee%20the%20scene%20unharmed%20but%2C%20thanks%20to%20details%20from%20an%20eyewitness%2C%20was%20identified%20and%20detained%20by%20law%20enforcement%20shortly%20after%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2014%2C%20Trump%20faced%20a%20closer%20call%20when%20he%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-butler-pennsylvania-rally-secret-service-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewounded%20during%20a%20campaign%20rally%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20a%20suspect%20perched%20upon%20a%20rooftop%20overlooking%20the%20event%20fired%20his%20rifle%20into%20the%20crowd.%20A%20rally%20attendee%20was%20killed%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-pennsylvania-rally-shooting-deaths-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo%20others%20were%20injured%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20shooting.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-was-thomas-matthew-crooks-the-trump-rally-shooter-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20Secret%20Service%20sniper%20killed%20the%20suspect%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20the%20July%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKenneth%20Valentine%2C%20a%20former%20Secret%20Service%20Special%20Agent%20in%20Charge%20who%20served%20under%20three%20presidents%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20security%20around%20the%20former%20president%20was%20ratcheted%20up%20after%20the%20July%20incident%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecret-service-scrutiny-shooting-donald-trump-pennsylvania-rally-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESecret%20Service%20faced%20intense%20scrutiny%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20failing%20to%20prevent%20the%20shooting.%20He%20said%20agents%20should%20have%20been%20on%20high%20alert%2C%20making%20Sunday's%20near-miss%20far%20too%20close%20for%20comfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDid%20we%20not%20have%20time%2C%20or%20did%20we%20not%20have%20the%20assets%20and%20resources%20to%20sweep%20that%20wood%20line%20and%20post%20it%20with%20a%20police%20officer%20ahead%20of%20time%3F%26quot%3B%20Valentine%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20to%20me%20like%20that%20would%20have%20been%20great%20business%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ba0533fe-c6b9-48f7-857a-0616a5af5d15%5C%22%3EStill%20doing%20Treasury%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EValentine%20%E2%80%94%20as%20well%20as%20Jeffrey%20James%2C%20who%20spent%2022%20years%20in%20the%20Secret%20Service%20%E2%80%94%20told%20BI%20the%20agency%20has%20been%20struggling%20with%20staffing%20levels%20and%20adequate%20resources%20since%20it%20was%20rolled%20up%20under%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20in%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%2C%20founded%20in%201865%2C%20had%20previously%20been%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20the%20Treasury%20with%20a%20mission%20to%20combat%20counterfeiting.%20Though%20the%20Secret%20Service%20no%20longer%20reports%20to%20Treasury%20officials%2C%20its%20agents%20have%20maintained%20investigative%20assignments%20related%20to%20credit%20card%20fraud%20and%20cybercrime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20the%20Secret%20Service%20should%20give%20up%20all%20of%20that%20and%20just%20be%20the%20executive%20protection%20arm%20of%20DHS%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20was%20making%20decisions%2C%20I%20would%20push%20them%20to%20eliminate%20all%20their%20investigations%2C%20aside%20from%20investigating%20threats%20toward%20people%20under%20Secret%20Service%20protection.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20both%20Valentine%20and%20James%20said%20they%20believed%20the%20agents%20are%20stretched%20too%20thin%2C%20forced%20to%20work%20absurd%20amounts%20of%20overtime%2C%20and%20said%20there's%20an%20incredibly%20high%20rate%20of%20attrition%20in%20the%20field%20that%20the%20Secret%20Service%20can't%20keep%20up%20with.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BWe%20never%20hit%20a%20time%20in%20my%20career%20where%20we%20were%20fully%20staffed%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20always%20in%20a%20deficit%20because%20you're%20always%20playing%20from%20behind.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20experience%2C%20many%20agents%20left%20the%20Secret%20Service%20before%20their%20retirement%2C%20James%20said%20%E2%80%94%20a%20natural%20occurrence%20in%20any%20field%20if%20people%20decide%20the%20gig%20is%20not%20for%20them%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bbut%20we%20were%20such%20a%20small%20agency%20that%20it%20really%20became%20a%20detriment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20tell%20you%20we%20had%20people%20driving%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpresident-car-limousine-photos-the-beast-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epresident's%20limousine%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20enough%20hours%20in%20a%20day%20that%20if%20they%20drove%20a%20truck%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-exec-surprising-reason-low-income-