ssues%2C%20which%20motivated%20him%20to%20work%20harder%20to%20provide%20a%20better%20life%20for%20them.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20we%20had%20the%20resources%2C%20we%20took%20her%20to%20the%20best%20hospitals%20and%20got%20her%20treated.%20So%2C%20I%20always%20focused%20on%20my%20studies%20because%20I%20strongly%20believed%20that%20through%20education%2C%20the%20happiness%20of%20my%20entire%20family%20would%20increase%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAbhishek%20credits%20his%20family's%20support%20and%20focus%20on%20education%20for%20his%20accomplishments.%20My%20parents%20and%20brother%20were%20my%20biggest%20inspirations%2C%20he%20said.%20He%20is%20the%20younger%20of%20two%20brothers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726566600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F9sb1e1l8_bihar-jamui-_625x300_17_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbihar-man-secures-rs-2-crore-package-at-google-s-london-office-6584057%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20computer%20engineer%20from%20Jamui%20district%20in%20Bihar%20has%20secured%20a%20Rs%202%20crore%20package%20at%20Google's%20London%20office.%20Abhishek%20Kumar%2C%20who%20completed%20his%20BTech%20from%20NIT%20Patna%2C%20will%20begin%20his%20new%20role%20in%20October.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbihar-man-secures-rs-2-crore-package-at-google-s-london-office-6584057%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'I%20am%20a%20rapist'%2C%20admits%20husband%20in%20French%20mass%20rape%20trial%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726566369000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1a2d%2Flive%2F537ff930-6139-11ee-b101-6f93d6dfbcc2.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcx2kdd3n7yqo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dominique%20P