%20of%20Investigation%20and%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20each%20of%20which%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20Mr%20Kejriwal)...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faaps-atishi-to-be-delhis-new-chief-minister-name-proposed-by-arvind-kejriwal-6583407%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll_Imagetopscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAAP's%20Atishi%20To%20Be%20New%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Chosen%20By%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtishi%20will%20take%20over%20after%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20-%20who%20dropped%20quite%20the%20political%20bombshell%20Sunday%20-%20meets%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20this%20evening%2C%20when%20he%20will%20formally%20resign.%20Her%20promotion%20was%20confirmed%20at%20AAP%20legislators'%20meeting%2C%20at%20which%20she%20was%20elected%20to%20lead%20the%20party'%20legislative%20council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2043-year-old%20MLA%20from%20South%20Delhi's%20Kalkaji%2C%20Atishi%20shot%20to%20prominence%20after%20ex%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Manish%20Sisodia%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case%20in%20February%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeteoric-rise-of-atishi-delhis-next-chief-minister-6583569%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeteoric%20Rise%20Of%20AAP's%20Atishi%2C%20Delhi's%20Next%20Chief%20Minister%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20handed%20charge%20of%20the%20Education%20Department%20led%20till%20then%20by%20Mr%20Sisodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20role%20grew%20further%20following%20the%20arrest%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20in%20the%20same%20case.%20And%2C%20after%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%2C%20Atishi%20and%20her%20colleague%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20were%20given%20key%20portfolios%20-%20he%20got%20Health%20and%20Water%2C%20she%2