Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDominique%20Pelicot%20used%20a%20cane%20as%20he%20slowly%20entered%20the%20courtroom%20in%20the%20southern%20city%20of%20Avignon%2C%20before%20sitting%20on%20a%20blue%20armchair%20to%20give%20him%20enough%20comfort%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20hearings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20rapist%2C%20like%20the%20others%20in%20this%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20Pelicot%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%2050%20other%20defendants%20in%20the%20mass%20trial%20--%20men%20he%20allegedly%20recruited%20online%20to%20rape%20his%20then-wife%20Gisele%20Pelicot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20all%20knew%26quot%3B%20that%20he%20was%20inviting%20them%20to%20rape%20her%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BShe%20did%20not%20deserve%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDominique%20Pelicot%20is%20accused%20of%20administering%20anti-anxiety%20drugs%20to%20Gisele%20over%20a%20period%20of%20almost%20a%20decade%2C%20from%202011%20to%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20was%20unconscious%2C%20he%20would%20rape%20her%20and%20recruit%20dozens%20of%20other%20men%20he%20met%20online%20to%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDominique%20Pelicot%20has%20admitted%20the%20charges%2C%20but%20Tuesday%20is%20the%20first%20time%20he%20has%20spoken%20at%20any%20length%20since%20the%20trial%20began%20on%20September%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20may%20also%20hear%20more%20from%20Gisele%20Pelicot%2C%20who%20was%20present%20in%20the%20courtroom%20alongside%20Dominique's%20brother%20Joel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeatrice%20Zavarro%2C%20the%20defendant's%20lawyer%2C%20told%20AFP%20on%20Monday%20that%20he%20was%20suffering%20from%20%26quot%3Ba%20clot%20in%20the%20bladder%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20kidney%20infection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20medical%20exam%20ordered%20by%20the%20presiding%20judge%20found%20that%20he%20was%20in%20a%20fit%20state%20to%20appear%20in%20court%2C%20avoiding%20a%20delay%20of%20weeks%20or%20eve