0survived%2C%20but%20the%20incident%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F266757%2Fneehaari-mandali-burn-survivor-mission-saviour-trust-kerala-ngo-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleft%20severe%20burns%20on%20her%20face%20and%20body%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20would%20take%20longer%20for%20her%20emotional%20scars%20to%20heal.%20But%2C%20in%20the%20following%20years%2C%20she%20would%20etch%20an%20inspiring%20story%20of%20resilience%20and%20overcoming%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Manisha%20is%20an%20influencer%20and%20an%20artist%20with%20a%20strong%20message%3A%20%E2%80%9CBeauty%20is%20not%20a%20face%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20what%20lies%20in%20your%20heart.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20road%20to%20recovery%20was%20not%20easy%20for%20Manisha%2C%20who%20was%20born%20in%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Jhajjar.%20She%20underwent%20multiple%20surgeries%20to%20recover%20from%20her%20physical%20wounds%2C%20but%20the%20trauma%20lingered%20a%20little%20while%20longer.%20Her%20survival%2C%20she%20says%2C%20is%20due%20to%20her%20family%E2%80%99s%20unwavering%20support.%20However%2C%20life%20outside%20her%20home%20was%20far%20less%20forgiving.%20At%20school%2C%20Manisha%20faced%20harsh%20rejection.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20classmates%20were%20scared%20of%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC_u5KIiS1UL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC_u5KIiS1UL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagra