by%20default%2C%20do%20very%20well%20in%20nature.%20My%20children%20are%20fascinated%20by%20nature.%20Being%20on%20these%20trails%20or%20hikes%20promotes%20a%20connection%20with%20your%20children%2C%20yourself%20and%20nature.%20You%20learn%20with%20your%20children%20and%20it%20ignites%20in%20them%2C%20a%20quest%20to%20learn%20more.%20The%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20that%20children%20are%20self-engaged%20in%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Rhituparna%20is%20curating%20a%20Meghalaya%20trip%20with%20Nehal%20to%20encourage%20more%20parents%20to%20get%20their%20children%20out%20and%20discover%20the%20unique%20bonds%20that%20are%20formed%20among%20children%20and%20like-minded%20adults.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20Nehal%20expanded%20Heart%20%26amp%3B%20Soil%20to%20include%20trips%20outside%20Maharashtra%20like%20wildlife%20safaris.%20Currently%2C%20she%20is%20planning%20trips%20to%20Meghalaya%20and%20a%20wildlife%20safari%20to%20Pench%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20After%20running%20it%20alongside%20her%20full-time%20job%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20it%20full-time%20in%202024.%20What%20sets%20her%20trips%20apart%20is%20that%20children%20of%20all%20ages%20are%20welcome%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20parents%20with%20toddlers%20to%20travel%20and%20enjoy%20nature%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20will%20bond%20as%20a%20family%20and%20understand%20each%20other%20better.%20Your%20children%20will%20not%20remember%20the%20gadgets%20or%20fancy%20gifts.%20They%20will%20remember%20these%20experiences%20that%20you%20gave%20them.%20It%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349527%2Fnew-mothers-online-support-groups-postpartum-breastfeeding-formula-sleep-training-parenting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edevelops%20their%20personality%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22