r%20Chorol%20recalls%20is%20from%20her%20undergraduate%20days%20when%20she%20visited%20her%20ancestral%20village%20called%20Skumpata%20(Lingshet)%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F302635%2Fladakh-ministry-of-education-score-new-heights-role-of-dedicated-teachers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELadakh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20about%2080%20km%20from%20Leh%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20struck%20by%20the%20ingenious%20traditional%20water%20management%20systems%20our%20ancestors%20had%20developed%20%E2%80%94%20the%20intricate%20network%20of%20channels%20and%20storage%20ponds%20that%20had%20sustained%20life%20in%20this%20harsh%20landscape%20for%20centuries.%20However%2C%20I%20also%20noticed%20how%20these%20systems%20were%20under%20threat%20from%20changing%20climate%20patterns%20and%20modernisation.%20It%20made%20me%20realise%20the%20importance%20of%20bridging%20traditional%20knowledge%20with%20modern%20scientific%20approaches%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FIMG_20230423_110238_478-1726233445-500x625.webp%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Lobzang%20Chorol%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FIMG_20230423_110238_478-1726233445-500x625.webp%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FIMG_20230423_110238_478-1726233445-240x300.webp%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FIMG_20230423_110238_478-1726233445-150x188.webp%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FIMG_20230423_110238_478-1726233445.webp%20736w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365885%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22625%5C%22%3E%3C