0%E2%80%9CI%20had%20so%20many%20dreams%2C%20and%20plans.%20But%20there%20was%20never%20space%20for%20anything.%E2%80%9D%20His%202.5%20ft%20mattress%20led%20him%20to%20wake%20up%20with%20back%20aches%20every%20other%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20he%20started%20Vinyasa%20Earth%2C%20he%20designed%20it%20to%20tackle%20the%20pain%20points%20that%20artists%20often%20experience.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20insistent%20that%20the%20stay%20should%20be%20both%2C%20comfortable%20and%20artistic.%20I%20thought%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20dancers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20mattresses%20at%20Vinyasa%20Earth%20come%20recommended%20by%20physiotherapists.%20They%20measure%20four%20feet%20in%20width%20so%20one%20can%20sleep%20well.%20The%20whole%20space%20is%20designed%20with%20a%20certain%20kind%20of%20flow.%20There%20is%20a%20story%20in%20every%20wall%20at%20Vinyasa.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FqndI7Cb9kvw%3Fsi%3DXpjhLA-iD3-09gO0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20draws%20at%20the%20stay%20is%20the%20amphitheatre.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20host%20numerous%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F116831%2Fmale-kathak-dancers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresidencies%20for%20dancers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20theatre%20artists%2C%20and%20filmmakers%20here.%20Teachers%20from%20across%20the%20world%20come%20for%20these%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sankalp%20sharing%20that%20this%20year%20they%20are%20keen%20on%20hosting%20a%20retreat%20for%20elderly%20people%20which%20is%20curated%20keeping%20their%20needs%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20aren%E2%80%99t%20watching%20(or%20taking%20part)%20in%20these%20residencies%2C%20there%20is%20much%20to%20keep%20you%20occu