e%20largely%20imported%20from%20China.%20%5BThis%20is%20because%5D%20Chinese%20chargers%20are%20priced%20low%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20support%20from%20Chinese%20manufacturers%20once%20installed%2C%20which%20is%20a%20key%20issue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Image-3-1725974308.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Plugzmart's%2060kW%20Fast%20Charger%20on%20the%20Left%3B%20Representational%20Image%20of%20a%20car%20charging%20on%20the%20Right%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Image-3-1725974308.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Image-3-1725974308-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Image-3-1725974308-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Image-3-1725974308-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Image-3-1725974308-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365373%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPlugzmart%E2%80%99s%2060kW%20Fast%20Charger%20on%20the%20Left%3B%20Representational%20Image%20of%20a%20car%20charging%20on%20the%20Right%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20miss%20the%20technical%20stronghold%20of%20the%20imported%20products%20and%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20resolve%20issues%20without%20service%20support.%20As%20EV%20adoption%20increases%20on%20the%20consumer%20and%20commercial%20sides%2C%20the%20requirement%20for%20chargers%20from%20manufacturers%20of%202%2C%203%2C%20and%204-wheelers%20and%20charge%20point%20operators%20is%20going%20to%20scale%20rapidly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%20The%20ARAI%20certification%20for%20their%20fast%20DC%20charger%2C%20which%20can%20offer%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fplugzmart%2Fp%2FC_EqU5GoKa7%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A075%25%20charge%20in%2030%20minutes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20another%20step%20towards%20addressing%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20speaking%20on%20the%20milestone%20of%20achieving%20this%20certification%20for%20their%20DC%20fast%20charger%2C%20Vivek%20Samynathan%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Plugzmart%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSecuring%20the%20ARAI%20certification%20for%20our%2060kW%20DC%20fast%20charger%2C%20especially%20with%20our%20controller%20card%2C%20is%20a%20significant%20achievement%20for%20us.%20As%20part%20of%20our%20broader%20vision%2C%20we%20are%20dedicated%20to%20building%20a%20comprehensive%20ecosystem%20of%20hardware%20and%20software%20solutions%20in%20the%20energy%20domain.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20goal%20is%20to%20provide%20end-to-end%20solutions%20that%20not%20only%20address%20the%20current%20needs%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F279874%2Felectric-vehicles-sustainable-india-battery-reuse-recycling-renewable-energy-ev%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectric%20vehicle%20sector%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20also%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333673%2Fbest-ev-startups-in-india-electric-vehicle-innovations-range-battery-technology%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efuture%20innovations%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20sustainable%20energy.%20By%20integrating%20smart%20technologies%2C%20advanced%20control%20systems%2C%20and%20IoT-enabled%20platforms%2C%20we%20aim%20to%20create%20a%20seamless%2C%20efficient%2C%20and%20scalable%20energy%20infrastructure%20that%20supports%20the%20global%20transition%20to%20greener%20and%20more%20sustainable%20transportation%20options%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDeveloping%20the%20fast%20charger%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Vivek%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20development%20of%20Plugzmart%E2%80%99s%2060kW%20DC%20Fast%20Charger%20began%20around%20the%20same%20time%20as%20other%20DC%20charger%20projects%20with%20a%20dedicated%20focus%20on%20high-power%20charging%20solutions%20initiated%20about%20two%20years%20ago.%20We%20went%20through%20approximately%20three%20prototypes%20before%20arriving%20at%20the%20current%20model.%20Each%20prototype%20underwent%20rigorous%20testing%20to%20refine%20efficiency%2C%20power%20management%2C%20and%20safety%20standards.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20these%20two%20years%2C%20there%20were%20multiple%20challenges%20they%20had%20to%20overcome%20in%20the%20development%20process.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20primary%20challenge%20was%20designing%20a%20proprietary%20controller%20card%20that%20would%20seamlessly%20handle%20high-speed%20charging%20while%20maintaining%20a%20compact%20size%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Founders-1725974442.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Co-founders%20Vivek%20Samynathan%20and%20Ragavendra%20Ravichandran%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Founders-1725974442.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Founders-1725974442-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Founders-1725974442-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Founders-1725974442-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Founders-1725974442-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365377%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECo-founders%20Vivek%20Samynathan%20and%20Ragavendra%20Ravichandran%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20does%20a%20controller%20card%20do%3F%20%E2%80%9CThe%20controller%20card%20manages%20power%20distribution%2C%20communication%2C%20and%20safety%20protocols%20during%20charging.%20It%20monitors%20critical%20parameters%2C%20such%20as%20voltage%2C%20current%2C%20and%20temperature%20to%20prevent%20overheating%20and%20overcharging%2C%20ensuring%20safe%20operation.%20The%20controller%20also%20enables%20intelligent%20load%20management%2C%20balancing%20power%20across%20multiple%20charging%20points%2C%20enabling%20simultaneous%20charging%20of%20multiple%20EVs%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ragavendra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAchieving%20efficient%20heat%20dissipation%20at%20such%20high%20power%20levels%2C%20minimising%20energy%20losses%2C%20and%20preventing%20component%20damage%20were%20critical%20challenges%20too.%20We%20also%20focused%20on%20ensuring%20compatibility%20with%20multiple%20vehicle%20models%20and%20integrating%20advanced%20load%20management%20features%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20One%20of%20the%20key%20issues%20with%20many%20common%20charging%20stations%20in%20India%20is%20their%20inability%20to%20cater%20to%20different%20vehicle%20models%20and%20their%20battery%20specifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20the%20charger%20work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Vivek%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%2060kW%20DC%20Fast%20Charger%20converts%20AC%20power%20from%20the%20grid%20into%20DC%20power%20using%20an%20internal%20rectifier%20(AC%2FDC%20converter).%20It%20delivers%20high-power%20DC%20output%20directly%20to%20the%20battery%2C%20bypassing%20the%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20onboard%20charger%20for%20quicker%20energy%20transfer.%20The%20charger%20communicates%20with%20the%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20Battery%20Management%20System%20(BMS)%20to%20determine%20the%20required%20charge%20level%20and%20adjusts%20the%20power%20output%20dynamically.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20further%2C%20Vivek%20also%20explains%20some%20of%20its%20key%20specifications%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPower%20Output%3A%2060kW%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInput%20Voltage%3A%C2%A0%20340-480V%20AC%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOutput%20Voltage%20Range%3A%20100V%20%E2%80%93%201000V%20DC%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEfficiency%3A%2095%25%2B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOperating%20Temperature%3A%20-20%C2%B0C%20to%20%2B50%C2%B0C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EComponents%20and%20standing%20apart%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20Components%20of%20the%20DC%20Fast%20Charger%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERectifier%20(AC%2FDC%20Converter)%3A%20Converts%20incoming%20AC%20power%20to%20DC%20power%20for%20faster%20battery%20charging.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECooling%20System%3A%20An%20advanced%20air%20or%20liquid%20cooling%20system%20ensures%20the%20charger%20operates%20at%20safe%20temperatures%20during%20high-power%20operation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EProprietary%20Controller%20Card%3A%20Manages%20real-time%20operations%2C%20safety%20protocols%2C%20and%20communication%20with%20the%20vehicle.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPower%20Filters%3A%20Ensure%20clean%2C%20stable%20power%20output%20by%20reducing%20noise%20and%20harmonics%2C%20enhancing%20overall%20charger%20performance.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20materials%20used%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20this%20EV%20charger%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAluminium%20is%20used%20for%20heat%20sinks%20and%20charger%20housing%20for%20its%20excellent%20heat%20dissipation%20and%20lightweight%20properties.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECopper%20wiring%20is%20employed%20for%20its%20high%20conductivity%2C%20ensuring%20minimal%20power%20losses.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC_UwVCiPIPq%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC_UwVCiPIPq%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC_UwVCiPIPq%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Plugzmart%20(%40plugzmart)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20does%20this%20charger%20stand%20apart%20from%20others%20in%20the%20industry%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERagavendra%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20charger%20features%20a%20proprietary%20controller%20for%20intelligent%20load%20management%2C%20allowing%20dynamic%20power%20distribution%20and%20simultaneous%20vehicle%20charging.%20It%20is%20specifically%20designed%20for%20four-wheelers%20and%20dynamically%20adjusts%20power%20output%20based%20on%20the%20connected%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20battery%20capacity%20and%20state%20of%20charge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20can%20we%20install%20it%20at%20home%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2060kW%20charger%20is%20designed%20for%20four-wheelers%20only%20and%20can%20charge%20a%20vehicle%20(with%20a%20larger%20battery%20pack)%20from%200%20to%2080%25%20in%2060%20to%2090%20minutes.%20For%20vehicles%20with%20smaller%20battery%20packs%2C%20it%20can%20go%20from%200%20to%2075%25%20charge%20in%2030%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20this%20charger%20is%20primarily%20designed%20for%20public%20or%20commercial%20use%2C%20it%20can%20be%20installed%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F247288%2Fhow-to-charge-electric-vehicle-explainer-ev-charging-station-infrastructure-lithium-batteries-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresidential%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20sufficient%20grid%20capacity%20(340V%2B%20AC%20supply).%20However%2C%20most%20homeowners%20may%20opt%20for%20smaller%20chargers%20(7-22%20kW)%20due%20to%20space%20and%20electrical%20limitations.%20For%20those%20who%20can%20meet%20the%20requirements%2C%20setting%20up%20this%20fast%20charger%20requires%20a%20robust%20electrical%20infrastructure%20and%20space%20for%20cooling%20and%20ventilation%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Ragavendra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDeveloping%20components%20in-house%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20components%20developed%20in-house%20include%20the%20controller%20card%2C%20PLC%20module%2C%20and%20software%20for%20load%20management.%20What%20is%20the%20PLC%20module%3F%20According%20to%20Vivek%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20PLC%20(Power%20Line%20Communication)%20module%20transmits%20data%20over%20the%20same%20power%20lines%20used%20for%20charging.%20This%20reduces%20installation%20complexity%20and%20allows%20real-time%20communication%20between%20the%20charger%20and%20the%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20onboard%20systems.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20PLC%20module%20enables%20the%20charger%20to%20negotiate%20with%20the%20vehicle%20on%20how%20much%20power%20it%20needs%2C%20ensuring%20the%20vehicle%20receives%20the%20optimal%20charge%20rate.%20It%20ensures%20compatibility%20with%20various%20vehicle%20types%20and%20allows%20the%20charger%20to%20comply%20with%20international%20charging%20standards%2C%20making%20it%20versatile%20for%20different%20environments%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20adds.%20In%20some%20systems%2C%20PLC%20modules%20are%20also%20involved%20in%20enabling%20%3Cstrong%3EVehicle-to-Grid%20(V2G)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20communication%20where%20the%20vehicle%20can%20return%20power%20to%20the%20grid%2C%20thus%20helping%20with%20grid%20stabilization.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC_TAZazIHa1%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC_TAZazIHa1%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC_TAZazIHa1%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Plugzmart%20(%40plugzmart)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20every%20component%20is%20developed%20in-house.%20Some%20are%20still%20imported.%20Vivek%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20source%20semiconductors%2C%20rectifiers%2C%20and%20cooling%20systems%20from%20trusted%20suppliers%20within%20India%20and%20abroad%2C%20particularly%20from%20China%20and%20Taiwan%2C%20known%20for%20their%20expertise%20in%20high-power%20electronics.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECost%20and%20customer%20base%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20single%20unit%20of%20the%2060kW%20DC%20Fast%20Charger%20with%20its%20proprietary%20controller%20card%20and%20PLC%20module%20costs%20around%20Rs%208%20to%20Rs%209%20lakh%20depending%20on%20customisation%20and%20quantity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20speaking%20on%20the%20customer%20base%20for%20their%20fast%20charger%2C%20Vivek%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20attracted%20interest%20from%20fleet%20operators%2C%20EV%20manufacturers%2C%20and%20charging%20network%20operators.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSeveral%20companies%2C%20particularly%20in%20public%20transportation%20and%20fleet%20management%2C%20have%20shown%20interest.%20We%20have%20received%20preliminary%20commitments%20and%20purchase%20orders%20from%20fleet%20operators%20and%20EV%20charging%20infrastructure%20developers%2C%20including%20local%20government%20initiatives%20for%20public%20charging%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20Plugzmart)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725976650000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Image-3-1725974308.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D365359%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chennai-based%20Plugzmart%20secured%20ARAI%20certification%20for%20its%2060kW%20DC%20fast%20charger%2C%20marking%20a%20key%20step%20in%20advancing%20India%E2%80%99s%20electric%20vehicle%20infrastructure.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20the%20charger%E2%80%99s%20proprietary%20controller%20enhances%20compatibility%2C%20safety%2C%20and%20high-speed%20charging%20capabilities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22With%20Startup%20%E2%80%98Fulva%E2%80%99%2C%204%20Friends%20Take%2024%20Types%20of%20Kozhikoden%20Halwa%20to%20The%20World%3B%20Earn%20Rs%2084%20Lakh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHamza%20Shaheem%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Kozhikode%2C%20recalls%20the%20very%20first%20time%20he%20was%20treated%20to%20a%20particular%20red%20sweet%20from%20a%20bakery%20near%20his%20home%20in%20Feroke.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20so%20good!%E2%80%9D%20he%20exclaims%20as%20he%20retrieves%20the%20memory%20from%20a%20treasure%20trove%20of%20others%2C%20all%20involving%20the%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20that%20childhood%20experience%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F308752%2Fdodha-barfi-history-story-of-wrestler-harbans-vig-tales-of-taste-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20confectionery%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20out%20of%20flour%2C%20butter%2C%20milk%20and%20sugar)%20became%20an%20important%20guest%20at%20Shaheem%E2%80%99s%20home.%20It%20was%20the%20main%20celebrant%20on%20special%20occasions.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20included%20festivals%20and%20dinners%20when%20relatives%20would%20drop%20by%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20smile%20that%20suggests%20he%20would%20gladly%20binge%20on%20the%20dessert%20every%20day%20if%20he%20could%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eaficionado%20says%20it%20formed%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20his%20growing-up%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20question%20begs%20to%20be%20asked%20why%20the%20natives%20of%20Kozhikode%20hold%20a%20reverence%20for%20this%20sweet.%20Shaheem%20credits%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20simple%20but%20unique%20taste.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20considered%20as%20an%20icon%20of%20Kerala%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1725528358.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Childhood%20friends%20(from%20L%20to%20R)%20Shabas%20Ahamed%20N%20C%2C%20Thesreef%20Ali%20P%20K%2C%20Sanu%20Muhammed%20C%20and%20Irfan%20Safar%20S%20started%20Fulva%20to%20retail%20authentic%20Kerala%20specialities%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1725528358.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1725528358-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1725528358-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1725528358-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1725528358-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364549%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChildhood%20friends%20(from%20L%20to%20R)%20Shabas%20Ahamed%20N%20C%2C%20Thesreef%20Ali%20P%20K%2C%20Sanu%20Muhammed%20C%20and%20Irfan%20Safar%20S%20started%20Fulva%20to%20retail%20authentic%20Kerala%20specialities%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20idolises%20the%20red%20variant%20(also%20the%20most%20popular%20flavour)%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eenjoys%20a%20gamut%20of%20flavour%20quotients.%20And%20understandably%2C%20Shaheem%20considers%20himself%20lucky%20to%20have%20lived%20and%20grown%20up%20in%20a%20city%20where%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20mass-manufactured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20we%20aren%E2%80%99t%20as%20fortunate.%20So%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20going%20to%20divulge%20an%20important%20piece%20of%20information.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20be%20limited%20to%20Kozhikode%20anymore%20to%20get%20your%20fill%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Not%20just%20one%2C%20but%20an%20eclectic%20mix%20of%2024%20varieties%20will%20find%20their%20way%20to%20your%20doorstep%20if%20you%20wish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20brainwave%20by%20four%20childhood%20friends%20is%20making%20this%20possible.%20Their%20startup%20Fulva%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Kerala-based%20brand%20serving%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F286270%2Fmom-sells-authentic-maharashtrian-food-in-mumbai-pune-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eauthentic%20traditional%20food%20products%20%3C%2Fa%3Esourced%20from%20small-scale%20producers%20%E2%80%94%20is%20completing%20a%20year%20of%20operations%20and%20has%20already%20touched%20a%20milestone%20with%20a%20Rs%2084%20lakh%20turnover.%20And%20as%20they%20share%2C%20their%20success%20story%20is%20written%20by%20the%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESquare-shaped%20pieces%20of%20history%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20visited%20Kozhikode%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20know%20it%20is%20almost%20a%20sacrilege%20to%20not%20return%20home%20with%20servings%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20also%20considered%20a%20%E2%80%98prestige%20symbol%E2%80%99%20in%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eas%20history%20tells%20us%2C%20has%20an%20interesting%20story%20that%20prequels%20its%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20supposedly%20an%20Arab%20invention%20born%20around%20the%2016th%20century%20when%20the%20community%20settled%20in%20Kerala.%20They%20were%20intent%20on%20gifting%20a%20piece%20of%20their%20culinary%20prowess%20to%20Kozhikode%E2%80%99s%20Zamorin%20(monarch).%20And%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Emade%20the%20cut.%20It%20went%20on%20to%20become%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20spice%20trade%20and%20eventually%20part%20of%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20gastronomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20have%20been%20perplexed%20as%20to%20how%20a%20simple%20blend%20of%20water%2C%20sugar%2C%20corn%20starch%2C%20coconut%20oil%2C%20citrus%20salt%2C%20and%20flavourings%20birthed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F281110%2Fmithai-map-of-india-10-lesser-known-indian-sweets-you-must-try-at-least-once%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20dessert%20so%20exquisite%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20no%20successor%20dessert%20could%20compete%20with.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20said%20that%20no%20two%20blocks%20of%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20the%20same%20as%20the%20ratio%20of%20each%20ingredient%20varies%20from%20proprietor%20to%20proprietor%20in%20Kozhikode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20tourists%20and%20locals%20aren%E2%80%99t%20picky%20about%20these%20changing%20nuances%20so%20long%20as%20they%20get%20their%20fill%20of%20the%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1-1725528601.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20combo%20box%2C%20that%20features%2012%20premium%20varieties%20of%20Kozhikoden%20halwa%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1-1725528601.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1-1725528601-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1-1725528601-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1-1725528601-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1-1725528601-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364550%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOne%20of%20the%20combos%20features%2012%20premium%20varieties%20of%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20was%20the%20case%20with%20four%20childhood%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20Shabas%20Ahamed%20N%20C%2C%20Sanu%20Muhammed%20C%2C%20Irfan%20Safar%20S%2C%20and%20Thesreef%20Ali%20P%20K.%20Growing%20up%2C%20they%20gorged%20on%20the%20sweet%20treat.%20They%20considered%20it%20a%20usual%20feast.%20But%2C%20it%20was%20only%20when%20they%20moved%20out%20of%20their%20hometown%20to%20study%2C%20that%20they%20realised%20they%20were%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20friends%2C%20who%20were%20studying%20in%20different%20colleges%20in%20Kerala%2C%20were%20berated%20with%20similar%20requests%20on%20each%20trip%20back%20home.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EEnikk%20kurach%20Kozhikoden%20halwa%20venam%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Get%20me%20some%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa)%3C%2Fem%3E!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20request%20came%20from%20teachers%2C%20friends%20and%20hostel%20mates.%20And%20so%20on%20every%20return%20trip%2C%20the%20boys%20would%20return%20loaded%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F210948%2Ffood-history-origin-of-halwa-ceremony-budget-indian-desserts-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecolourful%20squares%20of%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20were%20relished%20by%20its%20patrons.%20One%20day%2C%20the%20pattern%20was%20discussed%20over%20some%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20biscuits.%20They%20realised%20that%20people%20beyond%20Kozhikode%20and%20Kerala%20found%20profound%20delight%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20conversation%20furthered%2C%20it%20dawned%20on%20the%20four%20that%20while%20each%20had%20grown%20up%20eating%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20preference%20for%20flavour%20differed.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20there%20are%20so%20many%20flavours%20that%20existed!%E2%80%9D%20Sanu%20adds.%20And%20this%20sparked%20the%20idea%20of%20starting%20a%20platform%20that%20would%20be%20an%20umbrella%20of%20sorts%20for%20the%20different%20varieties%20of%20the%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%20a%20childhood%20treat%20into%20a%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%E2%80%99re%20planning%20a%20trip%20to%20Kozhikode%2C%20I%20encourage%20you%20to%20take%20a%20walk%20down%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EMittaiteruvu%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(Sweet%20Street).%20Also%20known%20as%20SM%20Street%20(SM%20stands%20for%20sweetmeat)%2C%20the%20lane%20is%20lined%20with%20shop%20upon%20shop%2C%20a%20never-ending%20blur%20of%20colour.%20Look%20closely%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20see%20the%20colour%20is%20lent%20by%20stacks%20of%20coloured%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Esquares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20street%20inception%20dates%20back%20to%20when%20the%20land%20was%20being%20ruled%20by%20the%20Zamorin.%20The%20ruler%20invited%20Gujarati%20sweetmeat%20makers%20to%20set%20up%20shop%20in%20the%20city.%20Today%2C%20it%20is%20a%20Pandora%E2%80%99s%20Box%20for%20%3Cem%3Ehalwas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20every%20kind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20friends%20fortified%20the%20idea%20of%20Fulva%2C%20they%20say%20nostalgia%20was%20a%20main%20ingredient.%20Thesreef%20pitches%20in%20here%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20if%20anyone%20in%20my%20family%20was%20going%20abroad%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20they%20always%20bought%20to%20take%20along%20was%20the%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%20We%20grew%20up%20with%20it%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337104%2Feasy-recipe-for-gajar-ka-halwa-history-winter-dessert%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edifferent%20flavours%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ehave%20always%20made%20us%20huge%20fans.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Irfan%20interjects%20here%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebeing%20in%20the%20market%20for%20the%20last%20500%20years%2C%20there%20is%20still%20no%20established%20brand%20for%20it%2C%20as%20is%20the%20case%20with%20many%20traditional%20products.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-3-1725528932.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20four%20friends%20at%20a%20Fulva%20pop-up%20store.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-3-1725528932.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-3-1725528932-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-3-1725528932-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-3-1725528932-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-3-1725528932-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364552%5C%22%20height%